Fitness Tracker Dashboard


A fitness tracking web application that allows users to log their workouts, set fitness goals, and track progress in a beautiful dark-themed dashboard.



Features:
User Authentication using Google OAuth (Login/Logout)

Profile Setup for the first-time users (age, height, weight)

Add Workouts: Track the type, duration, and calories burned

View Workout History: View past workouts in an interactive list

Calories Chart: Visualize progress with a line chart tracking calories burned

Responsive Layout: Dashboard with a clean 3-column layout for profile, workouts, and goals



Technologies:
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (ES6)

Backend: Node.js, Express.js, Passport.js for Google authentication

Database: MongoDB (MongoDB Atlas)

Charting: Chart.js for the workout progress visualization

Styling: Custom dark theme (using CSS)